---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home">
  <h1>Welcome to the FTC Portfolio Docs</h1>
  <p>
    This site walks you through everything you need to build a solid Engineering Portfolio - from the basic requirements 
    to actual design tips that'll help judges find what they're looking for quickly.
  </p>

  <h2>Getting Started</h2>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <a href="/lessons/" class="card">
      <h3>Lessons</h3>
      <p>Go through them in order or jump to whatever section you need. Each lesson stands on its own.</p>
    </a>
	<a href="/resources/" class="card">
	  <h3>Resources</h3>
	  <p>Helpful tools, example portfolios, and other resources to level up your portfolio.</p>
	</a>
  </div>

  <h2>What You'll Learn</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>What to put on each page</li>
	<li>How to match the judging criteria</li>
	<li>How to avoid walls of text</li>
	<li>How to style and polish your portfolio</li>
	<li>Good options for high-quality printing</li>
  </ul>

  <blockquote>
    <strong>Tip:</strong> A great portfolio tells the story of your season - the problems you ran into, the decisions you made, and the results you got. Focus on <strong>the journey, not just the final product.</strong>
  </blockquote>

  <h2>Quick Reference</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Section</th>
        <th>Key Focus</th>
        <th>Weight</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
	  <tr>
		<td>Team Presentation</td>
		<td>5 minute overview of your team</td>
		<td>15%</td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
		<td>Structured Q & A</td>
		<td>5 minutes of questions from this <a href="https://ftc-resources.firstinspires.org/ftc/archive/2026/event/question-bank" target="_blank">bank available online</a>.</td>
		<td>10%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Engineering Portfolio</td>
        <td>Record of your team's journey throughout the season</td>
        <td>35%</td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
		<td>Pit Interviews</td>
		<td>Judges visiting your pit and asking specific questions</td>
		<td>40%</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The above percentages are an estimation and can vary based on the specific judging panel and competition.</p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .card-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>